processingCommand.script:
:DEFINE &HOSTS#, string
!:SET &HOSTS#= ""
:SET &HND# = PREP_PROCESS_VAR("AE_test_read_only_DS", "KEY*")
:PROCESS &HND#
: SET &TMP# = GET_PROCESS_LINE(&HND#,1)
:PRINT &TMP#
:IF &HOSTS# <> ""
: SET &HOSTS# = "&HOSTS#,&TMP#" 
:ELSE 
: SET &HOSTS# = "&TMP#" 
:ENDIF
:PRINT &HOSTS#
:ENDPROCESS
:PUBLISH &HOSTS#,,TASK
